      "content": "i mean \"diminishing viability\" sounds a bit like a way of saying it's dying. if it's such a settled thing that coal is going away, then shouldn't the govt just stop subsidizing it altogether instead of making it a whole political fight? doesn't it make sense to just lean into the future?",
